h2 Formatting Help

#markdown-help
  h4 This page use Markdown formatting. Please refer to the guide below for help.
  hr

  p.bold General notes
  p Adjacent lines will be combined into a single paragraph.
  p To start a new paragraph, separate it with a blank line above it.
  p To enter a manual line break within a paragraph, end a line with two spaces.
  hr

  #markdown-details
    p
      b Paragraph Formatting
      br
      small These control symbols must be the first character of a paragraph.
      br
      small Heading symbols must be separated from their text by a space.

    h1
      span.bold.red #
      |  Heading
    h2
      span.bold.red ##
      |  Sub-heading
    h3
      span.bold.red ###
      |  Sub-sub-heading
    p
      span.bold.red @
      | Center align
    hr

    p
      b Inline Text Formatting
      br
      small These control symbols must surround and be in contact with the text to be affected, and must then be separated by blank space on either side.
    p
      span.bold.red
        | *
      span.italic Italic
      span.bold.red
        | *

    p
      span.bold.red
        | **
      b Bold
      span.bold.red
        | **

    p
      span.bold.red
        | ***
      b.italic Bold Italic
      span.bold.red
        | ***

    p
      span.bold.red _
      u Underline
      span.bold.red _

    p
      | Text with
      span.bold.red ^
      sup superscript
    hr

