      b Bulleted list
    p
      span.bold.red -
      |  Item 1
      br
      span.bold.red -
      |  Item 2

    p
      small
        | You must leave a blank line on both sides of a bulleted list.
        br
        |  You must leave a space between the dash and text.
      br
      small
        | You can indent items one level by preceeding the 
        span.bold.red -
        |  with two spaces
    hr

